{"tid":2498880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有人事顧問稱今年僱主聘用畢業生壓價或逾10%","createTime":"2021-04-21T12:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:44:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"01107412b7dbe2d79f9e2c451e7ae6bec2f626ea","tid":2498880,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"毅知顧問公司董事總經理周綺萍表示，隨著疫苗接種、疫情緩和，今年就業情緒較去年樂觀，但失業率高企，毋需經驗的一般工種平均每1000名求職者爭一個職位，畢業生月薪亦較前年最少跌逾5%，目前約11000至14000元。<br />\n<br />\n她指，由於部分去年畢業的學生仍未找到工作，勞動人口供應過多，預期今年僱主聘用畢業生時會壓價，幅度有可能逾10%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586849-20210421.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586849-20210421.htm&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=b8b16d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586849-20210421.htm&h=aeb1b841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586849-20210421.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4395dc95054659b0fa617067cbce0f6793ea314a","tid":2498880,"uid":45910,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"周綺萍呢啲蛆蟲幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591f0b04188e8373e75bbd0c65937669842d9ea2","tid":2498880,"uid":66324,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"未入黎已經知係周綺萍呢條不學無術的HR <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a1e03270d65041de1c9f1a728475796a2dd57","tid":2498880,"uid":185092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"又係條臭閪"},{"pid":"934f068349e7a39ae777497a2aefa4baa0fb01a0","tid":2498880,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"535a1e03270d65041de1c9f1a728475796a2dd57","tid":2498880,"uid":185092,"like":4,"dis